<li id="cite_note-pettit6265-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-pettit6265_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-pettit6265_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Pettit, Philip (2009). <i>Equity and the Law of Trusts</i>. Oxford University Press. pp.&#160;62–65. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/X978019956102" title="Special:BookSources/X978019956102">X978019956102</a>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.legislation.sa.gov.au/LZ/C/A/ASSOCIATIONS%20INCORPORATION%20ACT%201985.aspx">"Associations Incorporation Act 1985"</a>. Government of South Australia, Attorney-General's Department<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.legislation.sa.gov.au/LZ/C/A/ASSOCIATIONS%20INCORPORATION%20ACT%201985.aspx">http://www.legislation.sa.gov.au/LZ/C/A/ASSOCIATIONS%20INCORPORATION%20ACT%201985.aspx</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 17 October 2012</span>.</span></span></li>
